[b]Vegan Veronica's Baked Kale Chips[b]
[b]Ingredients[/b]
 - 1 bunch kale
 - 1 tablespoon olive oil
 - 1 teaspoon sea salt

[b]Instructions[/b]
 - Preheat an oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Line a non insulated cookie sheet with parchment paper.
 - With a knife or kitchen shears carefully remove the leaves from the thick stems and tear 
	into bite size pieces. Wash and thoroughly dry kale with a salad spinner. 
	Drizzle kale with olive oil and sprinkle with seasoning salt.
 - Bake until the edges brown but are not burnt, 10 to 15 minutes.

